{"tid":320723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波病逝】中共無恥 消息：逼家屬答應立即火化後海葬","createTime":"2017-07-13T17:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T01:32:15.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a670e051a484e1e52b3e5a7e3c91a019e5995b2f","tid":320723,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"異見人士北風凌晨在twitter發佈消息指，「果然，中國當局在逼家屬答應立即火化後海葬。」北風表示，當局總是能比你能想像的最無恥還要更無恥。另有接近家屬的人士稱，有聽過相關消息。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf6bb4ada5f9aaa120da6fb92f899189df4dd5b","tid":320723,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"毀滅證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8aa55b7a5a25d1a9c68ceb31abff0123e072b4","tid":320723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"BTW, 「北風」都唔係好人黎啦"},{"pid":"85d0496d04a078a76132b6a94a406bd9ae5b8b65","tid":320723,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"可能驚美國D 外星科技, 驗到D 骨灰有毒or有輻射.<br />\n索性倒落海等你check 都冇得check"},{"pid":"997db446967551c265ffc5f627fe162a79a24cfd","tid":320723,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"尋日家屬都係被迫簽字唔插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9661adea2cc9e5891c5d890646b14ca24bfbd89","tid":320723,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34ba44489c24d50fd7e370cee898ebb6f8de0e7","tid":320723,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfbe76396a2fc824bfdd0492026e11df252b185","tid":320723,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"人神共憤"},{"pid":"24d96f6b813205b4d67d223e54144ef3cda66314","tid":320723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日家屬都係被迫簽字唔插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔多鍾意你班人扭曲事情, 係事實先好講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170713/56948243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170713%2F56948243&d=a6RCAhb3gKlttboNOSdrqaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=22d5c2cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170713%2F56948243&h=8036b7e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170713/56948243</a><br />\n<br />\n【劉曉波病危】港專家斥插喉加重痛苦：你班大陸乜嘢醫生？<br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波在瀋陽中國醫科大學附屬第一醫院搶救，院方稱劉要插喉維持生命，但家屬拒絕。明愛醫院紓緩治療部副顧問醫生胡金榮，昨晚在facebook狠批院方的建議，加重病人痛苦，怒斥「頂你個肺，你班大陸乜嘢醫生？」<br />\n<br />\n胡金榮指出，劉不但末期肝癌，更「爆埋腫瘤出血」，插喉駁呼吸機只會延長緊病人痛苦，毫無必要，質疑提出此「治療方案」的人，根本不懂紓緩治療，「你唔識點樣幫個癌症病人走得舒舒服服，香港呢邊有幾十個醫生可以教你」。<br />\n<br />\n胡續稱，美國和德國專家已表明，醫生建議劉接受紓緩治療（palliative supportive care），但「你哋班人每插一枝針、每抽一枝血，我見唔到呢啲叫做palliative supportive care囉，我真係唔覺氣管插喉，以機械協助呼吸維持生命，叫做palliative supportive care，仲要講到家屬拒絕呢啲建議好似係佢哋嘅責任。好心，唔好再加重劉曉波嘅痛苦，可以嗎？」"},{"pid":"b6f8224a2d7db87699e8c5a196108931fd479daf","tid":320723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日家屬都係被迫簽字唔插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講還講, 唔係事實就唔好亂講<br />\n唔好學柴玲條八婆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170713/56949376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170713%2F56949376&d=a6RCAhb3gKlttboNOSdrqaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=09ae789d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170713%2F56949376&h=9d63e51a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170713/56949376</a><br />\n<br />\n醫生團體「杏林覺醒」今日就劉曉波病情發出緊急聲明，呼籲有關的內地醫護人員恪守專業，遵從普世認同的醫學倫理原則，還劉曉波有尊嚴的生活；並要求北京當局立刻無條件釋放劉曉波，尊重其出國就醫的意向，以及終止對劉霞的非法監控。<br />\n<br />\n該緊急聲明以《尊重自主‧停止傷害》為題，內容提到若官方公佈有關劉曉波的病情屬實（即其病情已達末期並不能逆轉），醫療團隊應當提供紓緩治療，緩解劉的痛楚。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為免造成進一步痛苦，醫療團隊亦有責任向病人及其至親解釋病情，盡量避免一切對末期病者弊多於利的治療，包括血液透析和插喉呼吸。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同時，醫療團隊應當承擔責任，貫徹毋傷害原則，不應推搪為「病人家屬拒絕插喉」，企圖將責任推卸到家屬身上。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又提到，醫學倫理原則包括「自主原則」（Principle of Autonomy）和「毋傷害原則」（Principle of Nonmaleficence），即是病人或其至親可享自由權決定治療方向和程序，「在詳細分析所有可行方案及權衡利弊後，醫療團隊應當尊重病人本人及其至親的意願，包括出國就醫的意向」；以及醫護人員不得做出令病人身心受害的行為，包括不必要之檢查或治療。"},{"pid":"9f67d3e998f2cd50bfb840c779ff7f72071462e3","tid":320723,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW, 「北風」都唔係好人黎啦</blockquote><br />\n我仲記得溫雲超條撚樣屌柒本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有記憶真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a5e98078b4f9699374021de7bbc7fea42f4378","tid":320723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BTW, 「北風」都唔係好人黎啦</blockquote><br />\n我仲記得溫雲超條撚樣屌柒本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有記憶真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記仇既人, 係痛苦既<br />\n<br />\n金魚記憶既人, 係快樂既<br />\n又可以忘記殖民者既咀臉, FB開STATUS啦"},{"pid":"6ee728220ebb80b765f